Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没怎么变？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那时起就只会说好热好热
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最大的槽点应该是小环吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们商量过的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 是她突然说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都吓一跳 当时原来还唱了歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时舞台上的所有人都懵了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一头汗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过乱七八糟这点倒是跟现在一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 完全没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,②Fafner名场面验证
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这个环节要来验证Fafner的名场面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我个人选出的名场面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望让大家来验证一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家先看影像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放影像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我还没说明完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是自动贩卖机 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离我的房间大约11步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常方便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人…还真是笨拙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是名场面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还有更多更有名的场面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如在手上画坐标什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名场面！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,验证
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去上个小号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么闲吗你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就那么闲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家请支持喜安先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石井君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边有空位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 只有这么窄的缝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,验证开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起身了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了恶梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去喝点清爽的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝点碳酸刺激的可乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请开始数数
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我数
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两步 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好讨厌的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会做那种梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五 六 七
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须好好研究一下深层心理才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八 九 十
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十一 十…到了 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了 果然有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请按下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按了可乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑咖喱？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…从那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑咖喱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜安先生 这个结论到底是非常方便还是不方便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常方便
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一项验证
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动尼伯龙根系统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.92,ZB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nibelung
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼伯龙根？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第一话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要验证这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 验证哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要验证哪个部分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要验证哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从最初 到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里已经觉得很…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即验证
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来想试试这里哪个最接近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}别动别动别动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 要两手都伸进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手指上有伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝天椒…会渗进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦正是祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好 说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天干得最好的一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那句说的好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 现在开始把手伸进尼伯龙根指环
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼伯龙根指环 朝天椒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:14:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 绝对不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该差很远吧 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸进去的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}喂喂你白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 伸进去的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 干干的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干干的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…然后 有痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来会痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是放进去也会痛？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了我有伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好痛 受伤的时候碰朝天椒真的很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子不要模仿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结论：很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼伯龙根指环 刨冰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不情不愿的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进不去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 塞进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:14:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结论：这个也很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼伯龙根指环 谜样啫喱？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要从哪儿插
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉？是这种感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好硬 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 哎这是什么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…谜样的啫喱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以拿起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出得来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到吗 有个手型
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样试了一遍 以一骑来说喜欢哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是选喜欢的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是一目了然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结论 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最接近尼伯龙根指环的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谜样啫喱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才松本小姐在这小声说 好想玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么厉害吗 你至于吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是破坏部件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,③冲方先生答10问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:17:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此介绍这个环节最受欢迎的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alvis不是有第一种职务和第二种职务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个第二种职务有什么选择标准吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有真壁司令真的有收入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得史彦应该是做什么都做不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以唯一能做的就是夫人教的做辘轳…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 那个算是他唯一能做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是他唯一…就说还算勉强能融入经济圈的手艺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一问 真壁家真的有收入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是大家都有支持爸爸…相当于皆城家的抚养家属一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲方先生你不是刚刚编出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过各个家庭应该都会觉得有趣而定期去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以Alvis的人们来看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个战斗之鬼竟然会做出这种可爱的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里偷笑着去买的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概千鹤医生之类的会一下子买个二十个左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那个月似乎会比较宽裕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
